BBVA Targets Controlling Stake in Garanti, Expansion Reports

-- B y   S h a r o n   S m y t h
-- 
2011-06-30T05:32:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-30/bbva-targets-controlling-stake-in-garanti-expansion-reports.html
Banco Bilbao Vizcaya Argentaria SA (BBVA) 
wants a controlling stake in  Turkiye Garanti Bankasi AS (GARAN) ,
 Expansion  reported, citing BBVA President Angel Cano.  The Spanish lender already owns 24.9 percent of Garanti and
will increase its holding over the next two or three years to
gain control, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sharon Smyth in Madrid at 
 ssmyth2@bloomberg.net ;  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Blackman at   ablackman@bloomberg.ne  